The paper deals with clothing retrieval using computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a self-learning visual attention model, which can also be categorized under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of limited training sets, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
